Project Title: restaurant-bill-generation-application

Description:

This project implements a restaurant ordering system using Python, SQLite, and customtkinter.

Python: Handles the application's logic, including data retrieval and manipulation.
SQLite: Stores persistent data for menu items, order history, and restaurant information.
Customtkinter: Provides a user-friendly graphical interface for menu browsing and cart management.


Key Features:

Interactive menu display.
Real-time cart management.
Order history tracking.
Restaurant information display.
Technical Details:

The Python code interacts with the SQLite database to fetch and update data.
Customtkinter is used to create a responsive and intuitive user interface.
